{
  "text": "Dendritic cell (DC) subsets express different sets of TLRs [CITATION_1] . We generated bone marrow-derived conventional (c) DC and plasmacytoid (p) DC in vitro. The responsiveness of these cells to hiSa was dependent on MyD88 and UNC93B1. Specifically, Tlr23479",
